Package embedding.nearestNeighbors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectedComponents
    A ConnectedComponents instance is used to work with the connected components of a graph given as AdjacencyList.
    KNearestNeighborGraph<T>
    A KNearestNeighborGraph object can be used to find the k most similar objects regarding a measure for every single object.
    NearestNeighborBruteForce<T>  
    NearestNeighborDescend<T>
    NearestNeighborDescend is a randomized implementation for KNearestNeighborGraph that approximates the nearest neighbor graph.
    NearestNeighborDescend.SynchronizedCounter
    Simple synchronized integer counter.
    NearestNeighborDescend.SynchronizedWeightedIndexSet
    Synchronized version of a TreeSet of NearestNeighborDescend.WeightedIndex objects.
    NearestNeighborDescend.WeightedIndex
    Representation of a single element as it is needed in the NNDescend algorithm.
